  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Faith in Action to tackle Gender Based Violence in Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This package contributes to the funding of a Safe House in the city of Ariquemes, in the north-west of Brazil, in the Amazon area. The Safe House focuses on protection and prevention, responding to needs, and ensuring that its prevention activities are founded in firm and relevant knowledge of the impact of Violence against women and girls on individuals, their partners and families, and wider society. Funds will come from the Scottish Episcopal Church for 3 years.</narrative>
  </description>
